<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: #e7f0ea;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .primaryColor {
            color: #0e6431;
        }

        .headline {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .titleSize {
            font-size: 1.0rem;
            font-weight: 400;
        }

        .textSize {
            font-size: 0.975rem;
        }

        .btnStyle {
            background-color: #0e6430 !important;
            color: #fff !important;
            border: none !important;
            border-radius: 10px !important;
            padding: 15px 32px !important;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            height: 54px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            font-size: 1.075rem;
            transition: all .2s ease-in-out;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .importantText {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0e6431;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <h1 class="headline" style="padding-bottom: 10px">
        This won't take too long
    </h1>
    <h1 class="titleSize" style="padding-bottom: 10px">
        Hi,
        <span class="primaryColor" style="font-weight: 700">
            <%=name%>
        </span>
    </h1>
    <p class="textSize">
        We’ve received a request to reset your shuttle bus account password. You
        can now do so by clicking on the button bellow. This link will expire in
        <span class="importantText">10 mins.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="textSize" style="padding-bottom: 20px">
        If you didn’t request this change or if you’d no longer like to create a
        new password, you can safely ignore this email
    </p>
    <a class="btnStyle" href="<%=url%>" id="myButton">Reset your password</a>


    <p class="textSize" style="padding-top: 20px">Best regrads</p>
    <p class="textSize">Shuttle bus team</p>
    <p class="textSize">
        If you still have some problem please contact us on :
        <span class="importantText">lorssyleang20@kit.edu.kh</span>
    </p>

</body>

</html>